Interface VirtualMachineScaleSet

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface VirtualMachineScaleSet
extends GroupableResource<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.ComputeManager,com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineScaleSetInner>, Refreshable<VirtualMachineScaleSet>, Updatable<VirtualMachineScaleSet.UpdateStages.WithPrimaryLoadBalancer>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure virtual machine scale set.
